                    }
                ],
                "civilopediaText": [
                    {
                        "text": "The Greeks are discussing the situation. At length.",
                        "link": "Buildings/Achaea"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "name": "The Loss of Italia",
                "text": "Italia is lost. The heartland of the Empire has fallen beyond imperial authority. Rome itself stands threatened, refugees flood every road, and senators who once debated tax policy are suddenly experts on military affairs.",
