                {
                    "name": "The Recapture of Italia",
                    "text": "Italia has been restored to imperial authority. The banners of Rome once again fly over the peninsula, and the roads are filled with celebrations, speeches, and officials explaining how this outcome was inevitable from the beginning. Historians will remember the victory. Accountants will remember the bill.",
